  "description": "Stage 3 Slice 3 fixed eval matrix. Hard cases gate the deterministic Course Architect / Lesson Writer / Tutor contracts; observational cases record non-gating metrics. Cases are executed by stage3_eval.runner against the real generation code with a fake provider (offline) or an explicitly confirmed real provider (observation only).",
  "cases": [
